<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٩٨٨. فَا أَمْرٍ اوْ مُضَارِعٍ مِنْ كَـ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«وَعَدْ»</span> … احْذِفْ، وَفِي كَـ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«عِدَةٍ»</span> ذَاكَ اطَّرَدْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٩٨٩. وَحَذْفُ هَمْزِ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«أَفْعَلَ»</span> اسْتَمَرَّ فِي … مُضَارِعٍ وَبِنْيَتَيْ مُتَّصِفِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٩٩٠. <span style="color:#6c6c00">«ظَلْتُ، وَظِلْتُ»</span> فِي <span style="color:#6c6c00">«ظَلِلْتُ»</span> اسْتُعْمِلَا … وَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«قِرْنَ»</span> فِي <span style="color:#6c6c00">«اقْرِرْنَ»</span>، وَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«قَرْنَ»</span> نُقِلَا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>* * *<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>